1
00:00:18,666 --> 00:00:21,500
- Happy:
PREVIOUSLY ON "FAIRY TAIL."

2
00:00:21,583 --> 00:00:24,500
- Natsu: NATSU! - Wendy: WENDY!
- Gajeel: GAJEEL!

3
00:00:24,583 --> 00:00:26,583
- Happy:
AND THE THREE OF THEM ARE--

4
00:00:26,666 --> 00:00:28,583
- Gajeel: DRAGON SLAYERS!
- Wendy: THREE BEST FRIENDS!

5
00:00:28,666 --> 00:00:29,583
- Natsu: FAIRY TAIL WIZARDS! 

6
00:00:29,666 --> 00:00:30,791
- Happy:
WOW, YOU GUYS REALLY NEED

7
00:00:30,875 --> 00:00:33,208
TO GET YOUR ACT TOGETHER.

8
00:00:33,291 --> 00:00:34,666
- Natsu: WHATEVER, WE WERE
TOGETHER ENOUGH

9
00:00:34,750 --> 00:00:36,041
TO KICK THE KING'S BUTT!

10
00:00:36,125 --> 00:00:38,041
- Wendy: EVERYTHING WORKED
OUT IN THE END.

11
00:00:38,125 --> 00:00:39,958
- Gajeel:
HEY, WHAT HAPPENED TO MY CAT?!

12
00:00:40,041 --> 00:00:41,458
- Lucy:
I HATE TO BUST YOUR BUBBLE,

13
00:00:41,541 --> 00:00:43,791
BUT THINGS JUST GOT
A WHOLE LOT WORSE.

14
00:00:48,666 --> 00:00:52,916
- ( theme music playing )

15
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,875
- ( singing in Japanese )

16
00:01:04,666 --> 00:01:06,083
♪ YEAH, YEAH, YEAH ♪

17
00:01:06,166 --> 00:01:07,416
- Chorus: ♪ YEAH, YEAH, YEAH ♪

18
00:01:07,500 --> 00:01:10,500
- ♪ THE ROCK CITY BOY ♪
- ♪ THE ROCK CITY BOY ♪

19
00:01:10,583 --> 00:01:13,416
- ♪ YEAH, YEAH, YEAH ♪
- ♪ YEAH, YEAH, YEAH ♪

20
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:16,833
- ♪ THE ROCK CITY BOY ♪
- ♪ THE ROCK CITY BOY ♪

21
00:01:16,916 --> 00:01:18,166
- ♪ OH, BABY,
YEAH, YEAH ♪

22
00:01:18,250 --> 00:01:20,625
( singing in Japanese )

23
00:01:40,916 --> 00:01:43,291
♪ MY PERFECT DREAM! ♪

24
00:01:51,208 --> 00:01:53,708
- Chorus: ♪ YEAH, YEAH, YEAH ♪

25
00:01:53,791 --> 00:01:55,250
♪ THE ROCK CITY BOY ♪

26
00:01:55,333 --> 00:01:56,333
♪ BOY, BOY, BOY ♪

27
00:01:56,416 --> 00:02:02,166
( singing in Japanese )

28
00:02:02,250 --> 00:02:03,791
- ♪ I WANNA BELIEVE
THE SING ON THE BEAT ♪

29
00:02:03,875 --> 00:02:05,291
♪ MOST RECENTLY 
IS LIKE RECESS TO ME ♪

30
00:02:05,375 --> 00:02:06,750
♪ PRETTY, PRETTY PLEASE,
NO BIRDS AND THE BEES ♪

31
00:02:06,833 --> 00:02:08,291
♪ BUT ECSTACY 
WITH EXTRA CHEESE ♪

32
00:02:08,375 --> 00:02:09,916
♪ RHYMING RHINO 
SOUNDING LIKE BONO ♪

33
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,416
♪ ALL SMACKED UP WITH
A BLACK JACK BOTTLE ♪

34
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:13,041
♪ WHEN I SAY "HO,"
YOU SAY "HEY"... ♪

35
00:02:13,125 --> 00:02:15,333
( singing in Japanese )

36
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:36,375
- LISTEN, THIS LOOKS BAD
BUT WE'VE GOT TO STAY COOL.

37
00:02:36,458 --> 00:02:41,125
LET'S HEAD INTO THE ROYAL CITY
AND SEE WHAT'S UP FOR OURSELVES.

38
00:02:41,208 --> 00:02:43,250
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY THAT?

39
00:02:43,333 --> 00:02:44,833
SEE WHAT?

40
00:02:44,916 --> 00:02:46,875
- IT'S OUR FUTURE.

41
00:02:46,958 --> 00:02:49,125
LET'S LOOK IT STRAIGHT
IN THE EYE.

42
00:02:49,208 --> 00:02:50,250
- ( gasp )

43
00:03:01,708 --> 00:03:03,791
- Mystogan:
TAKE ME BEFORE THE POPULACE

44
00:03:03,875 --> 00:03:05,750
AND EXECUTE ME FOR MY CRIMES.

45
00:03:05,833 --> 00:03:07,916
AS A CAPTAIN IN THE ROYAL ARMY

46
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:11,125
AND A MEMBER OF THE EXCEED RACE,

47
00:03:11,208 --> 00:03:12,375
YOU CAN QUELL THE CHAOS.

48
00:03:12,458 --> 00:03:14,416
BECOME THEIR SAVIOR!

49
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:16,708
YOU ARE THE RULER THEY NEED,

50
00:03:16,791 --> 00:03:19,625
LEAD THE PEOPLE INTO A WORLD
WITHOUT MAGIC.

51
00:03:19,708 --> 00:03:21,500
- DO YOU REALLY THINK

52
00:03:21,583 --> 00:03:23,041
THE ONLY WAY TO SAVE
THIS KINGDOM

53
00:03:23,125 --> 00:03:25,708
IS FOR YOU TO DIE?

54
00:03:33,625 --> 00:03:35,500
- ( Happy speaking )

55
00:03:37,375 --> 00:03:39,166
- ( screaming )

56
00:03:39,250 --> 00:03:41,375
- ( rumbling )

57
00:03:49,041 --> 00:03:50,958
- YOU MAY THINK
THAT THIS IS MADNESS,

58
00:03:51,041 --> 00:03:53,125
BUT IT'S OUR ONLY CHOICE.

59
00:03:53,208 --> 00:03:54,583
- ( groans )

60
00:03:54,666 --> 00:03:57,250
- BUT PRINCE,
THIS FOOLISH PLAN--

61
00:03:57,333 --> 00:03:59,916
HOW COULD YOU ASK THIS OF ME?

62
00:04:05,458 --> 00:04:06,541
- Pantherlily:
I SIMPLY CANNOT DO IT!

63
00:04:06,625 --> 00:04:08,208
- Mystogan:
I THINK YOU CAN.

64
00:04:08,291 --> 00:04:11,166
- THEN YOU OBVIOUSLY
DON'T KNOW ME.

65
00:04:11,250 --> 00:04:14,125
- DESPITE THE FACT
THAT YOU'RE AN EXCEED,

66
00:04:14,208 --> 00:04:17,208
YOU CHOSE TO SAVE THE LIFE
OF A HELPLESS HUMAN CHILD.

67
00:04:17,291 --> 00:04:21,083
YOU UNDERSTAND THAT LIFE HAS
VALUE FOR EVERY LIVING CREATURE,

68
00:04:21,166 --> 00:04:24,041
REGARDLESS OF WHAT FORM
THEY TAKE.

69
00:04:24,125 --> 00:04:25,750
- AND STILL YOU'D BURDEN ME?

70
00:04:25,833 --> 00:04:28,208
MAKE ME CARRY THE WEIGHT
OF THIS WORLD ON MY SHOULDERS?

71
00:04:28,291 --> 00:04:31,375
- YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
WHO COULD BEAR THAT WEIGHT.

72
00:04:31,458 --> 00:04:32,708
THERE'S NO ONE ELSE.

73
00:04:32,791 --> 00:04:37,375
AND I'M AFRAID THERE IS
NO OTHER WAY.

74
00:04:37,458 --> 00:04:41,208
- YOU ARE PRINCE OF THIS WORLD.
THE ONE MOST SUITED TO RULE.

75
00:04:41,291 --> 00:04:45,000
- I AM THE DESTROYER
OF THIS WORLD.

76
00:04:45,083 --> 00:04:47,000
- YOU'VE TAKEN
EXTREME MEASURES TO SAVE IT.

77
00:04:47,083 --> 00:04:49,750
YOU'RE EVEN WILLING TO PUT
YOUR OWN LIFE ON THE LINE.

78
00:04:49,833 --> 00:04:52,416
WE NEED SOMEONE WITH THAT KIND
OF HEART TO TAKE THE HELM.

79
00:04:52,500 --> 00:04:55,875
STEER US OUT OF THIS DARKNESS!

80
00:04:55,958 --> 00:04:59,541
YOU CANNOT BREAK THIS WORLD,
AND THEN LEAVE IT TO OTHERS

81
00:04:59,625 --> 00:05:01,541
TO PICK UP THE PIECES.

82
00:05:01,625 --> 00:05:04,458
<i>YOU</i> MUST MAKE IT WHOLE AGAIN.
IT'S <i>YOUR</i> RESPONSIBILITY.

83
00:05:04,541 --> 00:05:06,000
YOU CAN'T ESCAPE IT IN DEATH!

84
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:12,583
- Mystogan: THIS STORM
CANNOT BE QUELLED BY ME.

85
00:05:12,666 --> 00:05:15,083
- WHAT'S GOING TO HAPPEN
TO US, MOMMY? I'M SCARED!

86
00:05:15,166 --> 00:05:18,125
- WE'RE GOING TO BE OKAY,
I PROMISE WE WILL.

87
00:05:18,208 --> 00:05:20,083
- ( running )

88
00:05:24,583 --> 00:05:26,583
- COME ON, EVERYBODY.
JUST CALM DOWN!

89
00:05:26,666 --> 00:05:28,541
- ARE YOU KIDDING?
IN A TIME LIKE THIS?

90
00:05:28,625 --> 00:05:30,833
I'D START RUNNING NOW
IF I WERE YOU, LADY.

91
00:05:30,916 --> 00:05:33,708
THIS PLACE IS HISTORY!

92
00:05:33,791 --> 00:05:35,375
- IS HE SERIOUS?

93
00:05:35,458 --> 00:05:36,958
- WE'VE GOT TO GET OUT
OF HERE RIGHT NOW!

94
00:05:37,041 --> 00:05:38,750
- DADDY!

95
00:05:38,833 --> 00:05:39,875
- OH, THERE YOU ARE!

96
00:05:39,958 --> 00:05:41,791
- KEEP YOUR EYES ON YOUR KID,
OKAY?

97
00:05:57,416 --> 00:06:00,333
- Pantherlily:
I'LL DO IT.

98
00:06:00,416 --> 00:06:02,791
I WILL PLAY THE ROLE OF VILLAIN.

99
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:10,166
- ( explosion )

100
00:06:11,375 --> 00:06:13,541
- THE WHOLE THING'S
BLOWN TO PIECES!

101
00:06:13,625 --> 00:06:15,625
- OUR POOR, LITTLE HOUSE
IS GONE.

102
00:06:15,708 --> 00:06:18,500
- NOW THE BOY HAS NO PLACE
TO COME HOME TO.

103
00:06:18,583 --> 00:06:21,625
IT'S AN OUTRAGE!
AN OUTRAGE!

104
00:06:24,291 --> 00:06:26,041
- Pantherlily: WHEN I
WAS EXILED BY MY HOMELAND,

105
00:06:26,125 --> 00:06:27,666
THE KINGDOM TOOK ME IN.

106
00:06:31,375 --> 00:06:35,375
BUT NOW, I'VE RUN AFOUL
OF THE KINGDOM AS WELL.

107
00:06:35,458 --> 00:06:38,166
I'M A MAN WITH NOWHERE
TO CALL HOME.

108
00:06:38,250 --> 00:06:40,625
IF I'M TO BE SACRIFICED,

109
00:06:40,708 --> 00:06:42,708
THERE'S NO ONE TO MOURN ME.

110
00:06:42,791 --> 00:06:44,083
- PLEASE, STOP.

111
00:06:44,166 --> 00:06:47,875
YOU GAVE ME THE GIFT OF LIFE.

112
00:06:47,958 --> 00:06:50,083
I COST YOU YOUR COUNTRY!

113
00:06:50,166 --> 00:06:52,833
I CANNOT ASK YOU
TO SACRIFICE ANYMORE.

114
00:06:52,916 --> 00:06:55,458
- I FEEL THE SAME AS YOU.

115
00:06:55,541 --> 00:06:58,708
PLEASE, DO NOT THROW
YOUR LIFE AWAY.

116
00:06:58,791 --> 00:07:02,833
MORE DEATH WILL ONLY LEAD
TO MORE SORROW.

117
00:07:02,916 --> 00:07:05,375
AND MUCH MORE SUFFERING.

118
00:07:05,458 --> 00:07:09,083
- PERHAPS.  THEN HOW DO YOU
SUGGEST WE MAKE THINGS RIGHT?

119
00:07:09,166 --> 00:07:13,083
I'VE ONLY CAUSED MORE PAIN.

120
00:07:13,166 --> 00:07:16,125
- PANTHERLILY, SIR.
THE SITUATION'S MUCH WORSE.

121
00:07:16,208 --> 00:07:17,541
- I'M AWARE OF THAT.

122
00:07:17,625 --> 00:07:21,125
AS YOU CAN SEE, WE'RE DEALING
WITH THE ANIMA, HERE.

123
00:07:21,208 --> 00:07:23,375
- HAVE YOU STOPPED IT?

124
00:07:23,458 --> 00:07:25,500
- NO, NOT EXACTLY.

125
00:07:25,583 --> 00:07:28,458
- THERE'S BEEN MASSIVE RIOTING
IN THE ROYAL CITY.

126
00:07:28,541 --> 00:07:31,625
THE DESTRUCTION IS BEYOND
OUR CONTROL.

127
00:07:31,708 --> 00:07:36,541
- THE CHAOS IS FAR WORSE
THAN I HAD ANTICIPATED.

128
00:07:36,625 --> 00:07:39,041
WE MUST DO WHAT WE CAN
TO STOP IT.

129
00:07:39,125 --> 00:07:41,666
- Pantherlily: CONTROLLING THE
CROWD IS THE FIRST PRIORITY.

130
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:45,208
- YOU'RE RIGHT. WE CANNOT
LET IT SPREAD. WE SHOULD GO.

131
00:07:45,291 --> 00:07:48,833
- Soldier #1:
- UM, SIR?  WHO MIGHT <i>HE</i> BE?

132
00:07:53,916 --> 00:07:55,791
- ( screaming )

133
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,791
- ( whispering )

134
00:08:12,916 --> 00:08:14,416
- HOW MANY ARE THERE?

135
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,125
- Soldier #2:
THREE, SIR.

136
00:08:16,208 --> 00:08:17,583
- AND YOU HAVEN'T TAKEN
THEM OUT?

137
00:08:17,666 --> 00:08:19,125
EXPLAIN YOURSELF!

138
00:08:19,208 --> 00:08:22,541
- Soldier #2: YES, SIR.
UH... THEY'RE REALLY STRONG.

139
00:08:22,625 --> 00:08:26,416
- ( evil laughing )

140
00:08:32,041 --> 00:08:34,625
- I AM THE DEMON
THEY CALL DRAGNEEL!

141
00:08:34,708 --> 00:08:36,875
AND I'VE COME HERE TO THIS WORLD
TO STEAL ALL

142
00:08:36,958 --> 00:08:38,416
OF YOUR MAGIC POWER!

143
00:08:38,500 --> 00:08:39,500
- WHAT?!

144
00:08:39,583 --> 00:08:40,583
- NATSU?

145
00:08:40,666 --> 00:08:43,666
- Man #1:
OH, NO!  THIS IS HORRIBLE!

146
00:08:45,833 --> 00:08:49,250
- Natsu:
HAVE YOU GONE INSANE, OTHER ME?!

147
00:08:49,333 --> 00:08:50,250
NEVER MIND!

148
00:08:50,333 --> 00:08:52,750
- ( evil laughing continues )

149
00:08:52,833 --> 00:08:55,208
- FAUST AIN'T YOUR KING
ANYMORE!

150
00:08:55,291 --> 00:08:59,458
'CAUSE I KICKED
HIS SORRY, OLD BUTT!

151
00:08:59,541 --> 00:09:01,708
- ( evil laughing )

152
00:09:01,791 --> 00:09:06,166
BUT I DECIDED TO SPARE
HIS LIFE, FOR NOW!

153
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:07,750
- YOUR MAJESTY!
- OH, NO!

154
00:09:07,833 --> 00:09:09,958
- POOR KING FAUST!
- HOW DARE HE HURT HIM!

155
00:09:10,041 --> 00:09:13,791
- COME ON, RED FOX.
HEY, MARVEL!

156
00:09:13,875 --> 00:09:17,041
NOW, MY FAITHFUL SERVANTS,
IT'S TIME TO TRASH THE CITY!

157
00:09:25,541 --> 00:09:27,041
- HE'S GOT A SWORD FOR AN ARM!

158
00:09:27,125 --> 00:09:28,541
- IT'S ANOTHER DEMON!

159
00:09:28,625 --> 00:09:31,333
- WE'RE DOOMED!

160
00:09:31,416 --> 00:09:34,416
- THESE VILLAINS WON'T STOP
UNTIL THEY'VE DESTROYED

161
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:35,833
EVERYTHING IN SIGHT!

162
00:09:35,916 --> 00:09:38,541
THE CITY IS UNDER ATTACK
BY DEMONS FROM ANOTHER WORLD!

163
00:09:38,625 --> 00:09:40,750
- YOU BETTER RUN!

164
00:09:40,833 --> 00:09:42,708
- UH...

165
00:09:44,833 --> 00:09:46,708
- ( screaming )

166
00:09:50,125 --> 00:09:51,666
- I'M SORRY.

167
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:55,208
- JUST LOOK AT THEM, THEY'RE
AN UNSTOPPABLE FORCE OF EVIL.

168
00:09:55,291 --> 00:09:58,291
- ( chuckling )

169
00:09:58,375 --> 00:10:01,250
- ( crowd murmuring )

170
00:10:01,333 --> 00:10:04,625
- JUST WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING?  STOP THIS!

171
00:10:04,708 --> 00:10:08,250
- NOW, MY LOYAL SERVANTS
OF LORD DRAGNEEL--

172
00:10:08,333 --> 00:10:09,625
DON'T STOP DESTROYING STUFF!

173
00:10:09,708 --> 00:10:11,333
- KEEP GOING
WITH THIS SERVANT CRAP

174
00:10:11,416 --> 00:10:12,916
AND I'M COMING UP THERE FIRST.

175
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,916
- Natsu: JUST DO WHAT
I TELL YOU TO, SLAVE!

176
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,041
- I GUESS I SHOULD HAVE BEEN
MORE SPECIFIC.

177
00:10:17,125 --> 00:10:20,375
- ( thinking)
HOLD ON.

178
00:10:20,458 --> 00:10:22,208
- THEY'RE TO BLAME FOR THIS!

179
00:10:22,291 --> 00:10:24,750
THEY'RE THE ONES WHO STOLE
EDOLAS' MAGIC POWER!

180
00:10:24,833 --> 00:10:26,916
- IT'S ALL THAT
DRAGNEEL'S FAULT!

181
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:29,083
- Gajeel: THAT'S RIGHT, THE DARK
LORD DRAGNEEL'S THE BRAINS

182
00:10:29,166 --> 00:10:30,791
 BEHIND THE WHOLE OPERATION.

183
00:10:30,875 --> 00:10:32,166
- UNFORGIVABLE!

184
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:33,375
- GIVE US OUR MAGIC BACK, NOW!

185
00:10:33,458 --> 00:10:35,458
- BETTER BE CAREFUL,

186
00:10:35,541 --> 00:10:38,041
'CAUSE YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENS
WHEN YOU PLAY WITH FIRE.

187
00:10:38,125 --> 00:10:42,958
- Man #2: OH, NO!
- Man #3: HE REALLY IS A DEMON!

188
00:10:43,041 --> 00:10:44,083
- NATSU,

189
00:10:44,166 --> 00:10:45,958
STOP THIS, NOW!

190
00:10:46,041 --> 00:10:47,083
- HUH?

191
00:10:47,166 --> 00:10:48,750
- IS SOMEBODY CHALLENGING HIM?

192
00:10:48,833 --> 00:10:51,000
- HE'S OVER THERE,
IN THE CASTLE TOWER.

193
00:10:51,083 --> 00:10:52,208
- DO YOU KNOW WHO IT IS?

194
00:10:52,291 --> 00:10:54,083
- ( sighs )

195
00:10:54,166 --> 00:10:56,958
- ARE YOU TELLING ME WHAT TO DO,

196
00:10:57,041 --> 00:10:58,041
YOU LITTLE PUNK?

197
00:10:58,125 --> 00:11:00,125
- STOP THIS FOOLISHNESS,

198
00:11:00,208 --> 00:11:02,000
THE KING HAS BEEN DEFEATED.

199
00:11:02,083 --> 00:11:04,500
THERE'S NO NEED
TO ATTACK INNOCENT PEOPLE.

200
00:11:04,583 --> 00:11:06,625
- Natsu:
OH YEAH?

201
00:11:06,708 --> 00:11:07,833
- NO, DON'T!

202
00:11:07,916 --> 00:11:11,375
- IF YOU'RE TRYING TO SCARE ME,

203
00:11:11,458 --> 00:11:12,708
IT AIN'T GOING TO WORK.

204
00:11:12,791 --> 00:11:15,083
I DON'T CARE IF YOU ARE
THE PRINCE.

205
00:11:15,166 --> 00:11:16,208
- HE'S THE PRINCE?

206
00:11:16,291 --> 00:11:17,916
- COULD IT REALLY BE HIM?

207
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:21,291
- BUT THE PRINCE MYSTERIOUSLY
VANISHED SEVEN YEARS AGO.

208
00:11:21,375 --> 00:11:22,625
PRINCE JELLAL IS BACK!

209
00:11:22,708 --> 00:11:24,875
- Man: I DON'T BELIEVE IT,

210
00:11:24,958 --> 00:11:25,958
HE'S RETURNED?

211
00:11:26,041 --> 00:11:27,541
- Man #2:
JUST IN TIME.

212
00:11:27,625 --> 00:11:28,958
- Man #3:
IT'S A MIRACLE!

213
00:11:29,041 --> 00:11:32,625
- Pantherlily:
WHAT ARE THEY DOING HERE?

214
00:11:32,708 --> 00:11:35,375
- Nadi:
I'M RESPONSIBLE, SIR.

215
00:11:35,458 --> 00:11:37,000
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY THAT?

216
00:11:37,083 --> 00:11:40,208
- I HAPPENED TO OVERHEAR
YOUR CONVERSATION EARLIER.

217
00:11:43,625 --> 00:11:45,750
- LET'S FIGHT.

218
00:11:45,833 --> 00:11:49,583
OR YOUR PRECIOUS CITY IS GOING
TO GET BURNED TO THE GROUND.

219
00:11:52,083 --> 00:11:55,250
- IT SEEMS WE HAVE
OUR VILLAIN, DON'T WE?

220
00:11:55,333 --> 00:11:57,708
- WHY ISN'T THE ARMY
DOING ANYTHING?

221
00:11:57,791 --> 00:11:59,833
- SOMEONE HAS TO SAVE THE KING
OR THEY'LL KILL HIM!

222
00:11:59,916 --> 00:12:02,541
- IS ANYBODY EVEN SURE THAT
<i>THAT</i> GUY IS REALLY THE PRINCE?

223
00:12:02,625 --> 00:12:03,833
- I DON'T CARE WHO HE IS,

224
00:12:03,916 --> 00:12:06,041
AS LONG AS HE CAN BEAT
THAT MONSTER.

225
00:12:06,125 --> 00:12:08,458
- Panther Lily: THE CITIZENS DO
NOT BELIEVE IN THE PRINCE YET.

226
00:12:08,541 --> 00:12:11,666
- NATSU, STAY RIGHT THERE.

227
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:13,791
- DIDN'T YOU HEAR ME?

228
00:12:13,875 --> 00:12:16,375
I AM THE GREAT AND POWERFUL
LORD DRAGNEEL.

229
00:12:16,458 --> 00:12:19,583
- Pantherlily: IT'S OBVIOUS HE
WANTS TO MAKE JELLAL PLAY

