00:12:19,666 --> 00:12:21,000
THE ROLE OF HERO.

231
00:12:21,083 --> 00:12:23,916
BUT IF HE THROWS THE FIGHT
AND THE PUBLIC FINDS OUT,

232
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,666
THE CONSEQUENCES COULD
BE TRAGIC.

233
