- SIR, I'D ADVISE YOU TO BE
READY FOR SOME MAJOR SURPRISES.

235
00:12:33,916 --> 00:12:37,500
THERE'S QUITE A BIT MORE
IN STORE FOR TONIGHT,

236
00:12:37,583 --> 00:12:39,833
TO SAY THE LEAST.

237
00:12:48,708 --> 00:12:50,833
- OH, MY.
I FEEL MYSELF AGAIN.

238
00:12:50,916 --> 00:12:52,875
EXCEPT FOR THIS CRUSHING WEIGHT!

239
00:12:52,958 --> 00:12:55,958
I'M BEING SQUASHED BY MY MEN!

240
00:12:56,041 --> 00:13:00,333
WHAT THE DEVIL
IS HAPPENING HERE?

241
00:13:00,416 --> 00:13:02,666
IS THAT MAGIC POWER?

242
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:04,666
THE QUEEN,

243
00:13:04,750 --> 00:13:07,750
I MUST PROTECT THE QUEEN!

244
00:13:07,833 --> 00:13:12,291
- Nichiya:
( roars )

245
00:13:19,208 --> 00:13:20,791
- Gajeel:
THERE GOES THE PRINCE,

246
00:13:20,875 --> 00:13:23,750
IS HE REALLY GOING TO FIGHT
THAT MONSTER BY HIMSELF?

247
00:13:23,833 --> 00:13:25,708
WHAT UNBELIEVABLE COURAGE
HE HAS.

248
00:13:25,791 --> 00:13:28,583
- Woman #2:
HE'S SO BRAVE.

249
00:13:28,666 --> 00:13:32,416
- YOU IDIOT, I UNDERSTAND
WHAT YOU'RE TRYING TO DO.

250
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:34,583
BUT YOU'RE JUST GOING TO END UP
MAKING THINGS WORSE

251
00:13:34,666 --> 00:13:36,041
FOR EVERYONE.

252
00:13:47,125 --> 00:13:48,416
NOW SLEEP!

253
00:13:51,458 --> 00:13:54,791
THE ANIMA MUST HAVE
TAKEN MY POWER.

254
00:13:54,875 --> 00:13:56,666
- WHAT'S THE MATTER?

255
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:58,708
YOU SCARED WITHOUT
YOUR MAGIC, HUH?

256
00:13:58,791 --> 00:14:00,541
- ( grunts )

257
00:14:00,625 --> 00:14:01,791
- WELL YOU SHOULD BE.

258
00:14:01,875 --> 00:14:03,750
'CAUSE CHECK THIS OUT,
I'VE GOT PLENTY!

259
00:14:07,916 --> 00:14:09,875
- Man: EVERYBODY, RUN!

260
00:14:09,958 --> 00:14:11,291
- I SAID, STOP!

261
00:14:11,375 --> 00:14:13,666
- Wendy: NATSU, YOU'RE
GOING WAY TOO FAR.

262
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:15,250
- Gajeel:
NO, HE'S NOT.

263
00:14:15,333 --> 00:14:18,750
THE MORE POWERFUL THE VILLAIN'S
MAGIC SEEMS TO EVERYONE,

264
00:14:18,833 --> 00:14:20,125
THE STRONGER THE HERO LOOKS
WHEN HE BEATS HIM WITHOUT

265
00:14:20,208 --> 00:14:22,833
USING ANY MAGIC AT ALL.

266
00:14:26,875 --> 00:14:29,000
- LISTEN TO ME, NATSU.

267
00:14:29,083 --> 00:14:31,666
YOU'RE MAKING A BIG MISTAKE
WITH ALL THIS,

268
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:33,583
THIS WHOLE SHOW
THAT YOU'RE PUTTING ON.

269
00:14:33,666 --> 00:14:35,625
YOU CAN'T EXPECT
TO FOOL ALL THESE PEOPLE.

270
00:14:35,708 --> 00:14:38,833
- HAH, I CHALLENGE YOU!

271
00:14:40,208 --> 00:14:41,416
- Woman: PRINCE!

272
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:43,666
- Man: WATCH OUT,
HE'S DANGEROUS!

273
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:46,500
- YOU FOOL,

274
00:14:46,583 --> 00:14:49,500
YOU CAN'T BRING THE PEOPLE
TOGETHER LIKE THIS--

275
00:14:49,583 --> 00:14:51,583
THROUGH EVIL.

276
00:14:51,666 --> 00:14:54,791
- FIGHT ME FOR REAL.

277
00:14:57,916 --> 00:14:59,083
- YEAH!

278
00:14:59,166 --> 00:15:00,333
- YOU GOT HIM, PRINCE!

279
00:15:00,416 --> 00:15:03,416
- WE KNOW YOU CAN DO IT.
YOU'RE OUR ONLY HOPE!

280
00:15:05,708 --> 00:15:08,791
- YEAH, NOW THEY'RE
REALLY GETTING IN TO IT.

281
00:15:08,875 --> 00:15:10,958
- IDIOT!  YOU SHOULD HAVE
STAYED DOWN

282
00:15:11,041 --> 00:15:13,083
SO WE WOULDN'T HAVE
TO STRETCH THIS OUT FURTHER.

283
00:15:13,166 --> 00:15:14,250
- NOT MY STYLE!

284
00:15:14,333 --> 00:15:15,791
- ( groans )

285
00:15:15,875 --> 00:15:17,875
- OH, NO.
- GET UP!

286
00:15:17,958 --> 00:15:19,583
- HOW DARE HE STRIKE
THE PRINCE LIKE THAT.

287
00:15:28,541 --> 00:15:32,416
- ( crowd cheering )

288
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:34,375
- ( chanting )
GO, PRINCE!

289
00:15:37,708 --> 00:15:39,041
- THIS IS IT, BUDDY.

290
00:15:39,125 --> 00:15:41,416
I'M GOING TO GIVE YOU
A REAL FAIRY TAIL SEND-OFF.

291
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:44,583
SINCE YOU'RE LEAVING FAIRY TAIL,

292
00:15:44,666 --> 00:15:47,166
YOU'VE GOT TO SWEAR TO
FOLLOW THESE THREE RULES--

293
00:15:47,250 --> 00:15:48,791
NUMBER ONE,

294
00:15:48,875 --> 00:15:51,875
NEVER, EVER, SHARE SENSITIVE
INFORMATION ABOUT FAIRY TAIL

295
00:15:51,958 --> 00:15:54,041
WITH ANYONE,
AS LONG AS YOU LIVE.

296
00:15:54,125 --> 00:15:55,208
TWO--

297
00:15:55,291 --> 00:15:58,333
HOW'D THAT ONE GO AGAIN?

298
00:15:58,416 --> 00:16:01,500
- NUMBER TWO, YOU MUST NEVER
CONTACT ANY CLIENTS

299
00:16:01,583 --> 00:16:02,791
YOU MAY HAVE WORKED
WITH FOR THE GUILD

300
00:16:02,875 --> 00:16:04,083
FOR YOUR OWN PERSONAL GAIN.

301
00:16:04,166 --> 00:16:06,375
- THAT'S RIGHT,
AND DON'T FORGET NUMBER THREE.

302
00:16:06,458 --> 00:16:09,791
ALTHOUGH OUR PATHS MUST STRAY,

303
00:16:09,875 --> 00:16:12,000
YOU'VE GOT TO PROMISE TO LIVE
THE REST OF YOUR LIFE

304
00:16:12,083 --> 00:16:13,416
TO THE FULLEST.

305
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:17,000
THAT MEANS TO TREAT EVERY DAY
LIKE IT WAS GOING TO BE

306
00:16:17,083 --> 00:16:19,708
YOUR LAST DAY IN THIS WORLD.

307
00:16:19,791 --> 00:16:21,250
DON'T FORGET THE FRIENDS
YOU LOVED.

308
00:16:21,333 --> 00:16:25,416
- YOU MUST TREASURE THEM
FOR AS LONG AS YOU LIVE.

309
00:16:36,250 --> 00:16:39,333
- DID YOU GET ALL THAT?

310
00:16:42,333 --> 00:16:44,708
- Natsu: WHEN A GUILD
WORKS TOGETHER,

311
00:16:44,791 --> 00:16:46,916
THERE'S NOTHING THEY CAN'T DO.

312
00:16:49,791 --> 00:16:52,500
NICE KNOWING YOU, PAL.
LATER.

313
00:16:52,583 --> 00:16:54,458
- ( crowd cheering )

314
00:16:58,625 --> 00:17:00,500
- THANK YOU.

315
00:17:00,583 --> 00:17:02,458
- Man: THE PRINCE WON!

316
00:17:02,541 --> 00:17:03,541
- Man #2: HE BEAT HIM!

317
00:17:03,625 --> 00:17:04,666
- Man #3: AWESOME!

318
00:17:04,750 --> 00:17:05,958
- Woman: PRINCE, YOU'RE MY HERO!

319
00:17:10,083 --> 00:17:12,166
- NATSU.

320
00:17:29,958 --> 00:17:32,166
- WHAT?

321
00:17:32,250 --> 00:17:33,333
WHAT'S THAT?

322
00:17:33,416 --> 00:17:35,458
- IT'S STARTING.

323
00:17:35,541 --> 00:17:37,541
- YEAH, I GUESS
OUR LITTLE SONG AND DANCE

324
00:17:37,625 --> 00:17:38,541
AIN'T OVER JUST YET.

325
00:17:38,625 --> 00:17:40,000
- Man: DO YOU SEE THAT?

326
00:17:40,083 --> 00:17:41,916
- Woman: HIS BODY IS GLOWING.

327
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:44,500
- WHAT'S HAPPENING TO US?

328
00:17:44,583 --> 00:17:46,958
- THE REVERSE ANIMA SPELL
IS BEGINNING TO CAST

329
00:17:47,041 --> 00:17:49,291
EVERY REMAINING SHRED OF MAGIC
OUT OF EDOLAS.

330
00:17:49,375 --> 00:17:51,750
AND BECAUSE WE POSSESS
INTERNAL MAGIC POWERS,

331
00:17:51,833 --> 00:17:54,666
THAT INCLUDES ALL OF THE EXCEEDS
AND THE DRAGON SLAYERS AS WELL.

332
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:58,125
WE'LL ALL BE PULLED
INTO EARTH LAND.

333
00:17:58,208 --> 00:17:59,875
- SAY WHAT?

334
00:17:59,958 --> 00:18:01,833
- I BELIEVE THE
QUEEN IS PREPARING

335
00:18:01,916 --> 00:18:03,666
FOR THIS OCCURRENCE AS WE SPEAK.

336
00:18:06,583 --> 00:18:08,666
- I'M SCARED, YOUR HIGHNESS.

337
00:18:08,750 --> 00:18:10,250
- I'M FEELING REALLY WEIRD.

338
00:18:10,333 --> 00:18:12,833
- Chagot: DON'T BE AFRAID,
IT WILL BE ALRIGHT.

339
00:18:12,916 --> 00:18:17,708
THEY DON'T NEED ANGELS NOW,
SO WE HAVE TO MOVE ALONG.

340
00:18:17,791 --> 00:18:19,708
THERE'S GOING TO BE
A BIG CHANGE FOR US.

341
00:18:19,791 --> 00:18:22,625
AND WE ALL HAVE TO WALK
TOWARDS IT WITH A BRAVE FACE.

342
00:18:22,708 --> 00:18:24,875
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

343
00:18:24,958 --> 00:18:26,125
- I HAVE NO IDEA.

344
00:18:26,208 --> 00:18:28,916
- THE ANIMA IS PULLING US
OUT OF THIS WORLD!

345
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:31,416
- ( gasping )

346
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:41,333
- Lucy: IT LOOKS LIKE THE ANIMA
IS STARTING TO WORK IN REVERSE

347
00:18:41,416 --> 00:18:43,416
AND IT'S PUSHING THE MAGIC
OUT OF HERE.

348
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:45,416
THAT MEANS WE'VE
GOT TO GO, TOO.

349
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:48,625
- Natsu:
HEY, WHAT'S UP, YOU GUYS?

350
00:18:48,708 --> 00:18:49,833
- Lucy: NATSU!
- Happy: NATSU!

351
00:18:49,916 --> 00:18:52,166
- Gray: GOOD TO SEE
YOU, PAL. YOU'RE OK.

352
00:18:52,250 --> 00:18:54,166
- THIS IS CRAZY!

353
00:18:54,250 --> 00:18:56,166
- Alzack:
I GUESS IT'S FINALLY HAPPENING.

354
00:18:56,250 --> 00:18:58,750
WE'RE LOSING
OUR MAGIC POWER, FOREVER!

355
00:18:58,833 --> 00:19:00,916
- Bisca: DOES THIS MEAN WE'RE
GOING TO LOSE OUR GUILD, TOO?

356
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:04,375
- I'M SO SCARED.
WHATEVER WILL BECOME OF US, NOW?

357
00:19:04,458 --> 00:19:07,083
- YOU'RE ASKING ME, LIKE I'VE
GOT SOME KIND OF ANSWER?

358
00:19:07,166 --> 00:19:09,375
- TRY NOT TO WORRY ABOUT IT,
YOU GUYS.

359
00:19:09,458 --> 00:19:11,500
IT TAKES A HECK OF A LOT MORE
THAN JUST MAGIC

360
00:19:11,583 --> 00:19:13,500
TO MAKE A REAL GUILD,
TRUST ME.

361
00:19:17,083 --> 00:19:20,500
IT'S ALL ABOUT FRIENDSHIP.
THAT'S THE HEART OF A GUILD.

362
00:19:33,666 --> 00:19:35,958
- IS THIS IT, SCARLET?

363
00:19:36,041 --> 00:19:37,125
- I'M AFRAID SO, NIGHTWALKER.

364
00:19:43,583 --> 00:19:45,750
NO. WE'RE BOTH--

365
00:19:45,833 --> 00:19:48,708
- ( both )
ERZA.

366
00:19:50,708 --> 00:19:55,000
- Lucky: WHAT IN TARNATION
IS GOING ON HERE?

367
00:19:55,083 --> 00:19:56,500
- THIS FORCE IS PULLING US IN!

368
00:19:56,583 --> 00:19:59,333
- THIS CANNOT BE!
JUST WHEN WE WERE REVIVED

369
00:19:59,416 --> 00:20:02,083
AND READY TO PERFORM FEATS
OF UNIMAGINABLE HEROISM!

370
00:20:02,166 --> 00:20:03,541
- SIR, YES, SIR!

371
00:20:09,375 --> 00:20:14,000
- ( screaming )

372
00:20:14,083 --> 00:20:17,375
- Mystogan: I KNEW
THE MAGIC WOULD BE EXPELLED.

373
00:20:17,458 --> 00:20:21,208
BUT I HAD NO IDEA THE PEOPLE
WOULD BE AS WELL.

374
00:20:21,291 --> 00:20:24,291
- WHOA, HE TOTALLY SENT
THE BAD GUYS FLYING AWAY!

375
00:20:24,375 --> 00:20:26,916
- THE PRINCE JUST SAVED
THE ENTIRE KINGDOM!

376
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,083
- Man: OH, YEAH!

377
00:20:28,166 --> 00:20:29,916
- HERO OF THE KINGDOM!

378
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,916
- Pantherlily:
PRINCE.

379
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:34,916
ALTHOUGH THINGS ARE
CHANGING RAPIDLY,

380
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:37,791
DON'T FORGET, ADAPTING
TO THEM CAN TAKE TIME.

381
00:20:37,875 --> 00:20:39,458
DON'T RUSH.

382
00:20:39,541 --> 00:20:42,541
LEAD YOUR PEOPLE WITH WARMTH
AND A CALM HEART.

383
00:20:42,625 --> 00:20:45,000
TAKE THEM AT A PACE
THEY CAN KEEP UP WITH.

384
00:20:45,083 --> 00:20:48,333
THEY WILL MARCH ALONGSIDE YOU
INTO THE FUTURE.

385
00:20:48,416 --> 00:20:51,500
- I WILL.

386
00:20:51,583 --> 00:20:54,083
- BYE-BYE, LUCY ASHLEY!

387
00:20:54,166 --> 00:20:56,166
BYE, EVERYBODY IN FAIRY TAIL!

388
00:20:58,250 --> 00:21:01,125
- LATER!
AND BEST OF LUCK TO ME!

389
00:21:01,208 --> 00:21:03,291
