00:21:07,291 --> 00:21:10,166
- YOU MAKE IT SOUND LIKE IT'S
CONFUSING OR SOMETHING.

392
00:21:10,250 --> 00:21:12,666
- BYE-BYE, PRINCESS.
TAKE CARE UP THERE.

393
00:21:12,750 --> 00:21:15,000
- BYE-BYE, EVERYONE.
WE'LL SEE YOU LATER.

394
00:21:15,083 --> 00:21:19,000
- DON'T BE SUCH A FOOL, WE WON'T
BE SEEING THEM AGAIN. NEVER.

395
00:21:19,083 --> 00:21:20,333
- WHAT?!

396
00:21:20,416 --> 00:21:24,083
( crying )
I'LL MISS YOU!

397
00:21:24,166 --> 00:21:26,583
- STOP BEING SO SENTIMENTAL.

398
00:21:26,666 --> 00:21:28,208
IT'S JUST PATHETIC.

399
00:21:29,833 --> 00:21:34,958
- Lucy: AND WITH THAT, WE
ALL WENT BACK TO EARTH LAND.

400
00:21:35,041 --> 00:21:38,375
- FAREWELL, PRINCE.

401
00:21:38,458 --> 00:21:41,708
- FAREWELL, LILY.

402
00:21:41,791 --> 00:21:45,375
AND FAREWELL TO MY FAMILY
IN FAIRY TAIL.

403
00:21:45,458 --> 00:21:48,916
I'LL CHERISH OUR MEMORIES
FOR AS LONG AS I LIVE.

404
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:51,416
I PROMISE I WILL.

405
00:22:01,375 --> 00:22:02,875
- Lucy: YOU CAN'T HELP BUT
WONDER WHAT WENT DOWN

406
00:22:02,958 --> 00:22:04,208
AFTER WE LEFT.

407
00:22:12,875 --> 00:22:16,125
- THE MONSTERS
HAVE BEEN DEFEATED!

408
00:22:16,208 --> 00:22:19,500
WHETHER WE HAVE MAGIC OR NOT,
OUR KINGDOM WILL LIVE ON

409
00:22:19,583 --> 00:22:22,125
SAFELY AND PEACEFULLY
FOR ALL ETERNITY!

410
00:22:22,208 --> 00:22:26,750
- ( crowd cheering )

411
00:22:29,458 --> 00:22:31,083
- Lucy: I HAVE A FEELING
THINGS ARE GOING TO BE

412
00:22:31,166 --> 00:22:34,000
A WHOLE LOT BETTER
FOR THEM.

413
00:22:34,083 --> 00:22:38,125
