00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:17,916
- Happy: I HOPE EVERYONE
MADE IT BACK OK.

419
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:18,958
- Natsu: DON'T WORRY,
LITTLE BUDDY.

420
00:24:19,041 --> 00:24:20,250
